item.description: My journey to Cyber Security started with a BA in Psychology, an AS in Computer Science, and recently starting graduate school in the Fall of 2021. I’m currently enrolled in GA Tech’s OMSCS program, with an expected graduation date of Fall 2024. My current interests are in the areas of Capture The Flag (CTF) competitions and Penetration Testing, which includes privilege escalation in Linux and Windows and Open Source Intelligence (OSINT).
